  "texts": [
    "In the three above aspects, namely cohesion across sentences, coherence of ideas, and organization of text, the Means are from 4.05 to 4.25.",
    "It suggests that a majority of the students agree that these three traits are problematic to them and need treatment.",
    "From the interview with the teachers, the researcher was informed that students could only use simple, cohesive devices, but some of them still made mistakes like using unparalleled linking words such as \"firstly,\" then, \"second,\" \"third,\" etc.",
    "Furthermore, the organization and flow of ideas were not good as the students still struggled to generate ideas, and even when they could find ideas for writing, they still arranged them illogically.",
    "In Table 7, the Means from 4.00 to 4.45 indicate that a great number of the students agreed that they needed more knowledge of Vocabulary."
